m English domination. The altered short form <i>Bob</i> is very common, but <i>Hob</i> and <i>Dob</i>, which were common in the Middle Ages and gave rise to surnames, are extinct.  See also  Rupert ."],"variants":[]}],"lifeSummary":"When Robert de Wallers was born in 1135, in France, his father, Henri de Wallers, was 31 and his mother, Giselberthe de Bavay, was 16. He had at least 1 son with Jeanne de Avesnes. He died in 1192, at the age of 57."},"et":{"1135–1192":"1135–1192","1149–1203":"1149–1203","1168–1205":"1168–1205","1104–1167":"1104–1167","1119–Female":"1119–Surnud","1205":"1205","1149":"1149","1104":"1104","1203":"1203","1135":"1135","1168":"1168","1167":"1167","1192":"1192","1119":"1119","France":"Prantsusmaa"},"fi":{"1135–1192":"1135–1192","1149–1203":"1149–1203","1168–1205":"1168–1205","1104–1167":"1104–1167","1119–Female":"1119–Kuollut","1205":"1205","1149":"1149","1104":"1104","1203":"1203","1135":"1135","1168":"1168","1167":"1167","1192":"1192","1119":"1119","France":"Ranska"},"fr":{"1135–1192":"1135–1192","1149–1203":"1149–1203","1168–1205":"1168–1205","1104–1167":"1104–1167","1119–Female":"1119–Décédée","1205":"1205","1149":"1149","1104":"1104","1203":"1203","1135":"1135","1168":"1168","1167":"1167","1192":"1192","1119":"1119","France":"France","lifeSummary":"Lorsque Robert de Wallers est né en 1135, à France, son père, Henri de Wallers, avait 31 ans et sa mère, Giselberthe de Bavay, avait 16 ans. Il a eu au moins 1 fils avec Jeanne de Avesnes. Il est décédé en 1192, à l’âge de 57 ans."},"de":{"1135–1192":"1135–1192","1149–1203":"1149–1203","1168–1205":"1168–1205","1104–1167":"1104–1167","1119–Female":"1119–Verstorben","1205":"1205","1149":"1149","1104":"1104","1203":"1203","1135":"1135","1168":"1168","1167":"1167","1192":"1192","1119":"1119","France":"Frankreich","lifeSummary":"Als Robert de Wallers 1135 in Frankreich geboren wurde, war sein Vater Henri de Wallers 31 und seine Mutter Giselberthe de Bavay 16. Er hatte mit Jeanne de Avesnes mindesten